In order to receive the COVID-19 vaccination, you’ll need to sign up for a complimentary One Medical trial membership. This allows you to use One Medical’s app or website to book your  appointment, get appointment reminders, and access virtual care if you need it. Sign up and download the app. This trial membership should cover the time required to receive both doses of the vaccine, and is available only to those referred by the WA DPH who are currently eligible for vaccination. A trial membership does not guarantee an appointment or other access to COVID-19 vaccines.
